      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAYWYN'S NOBLE (5) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at this track over 457m behind Red Tape (26.22) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Can bounce back. DAYTONA SUNSET (2) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (25.56) at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Can feature again. MILCHICK (8) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (20.14) in a P5 at Capalaba latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Well placed here and can atone this time. ICE RIDER (4) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.",
